flowchart TD
    Webhook([Webhook: Deal Sales Closed<br/>POST /hubspot-deal-closed-se]) --> Normalize[Normalize Webhook Data<br/>Extract dealId]
    Normalize --> FetchDeal[Fetch Deal Details<br/>GET /deals + properties]
    FetchDeal --> CheckSE{SE Assigned?<br/>solutions_engineer<br/>not empty}
    CheckSE -->|No| Stop1([No Op])
    CheckSE -->|Yes| ResolveSE[Resolve SE Name<br/>GET /owners]
    ResolveSE --> SlackLookup[Lookup SE in Slack<br/>users.lookupByEmail]
    SlackLookup --> SearchLinear[Search Linear for Ticket<br/>GraphQL attachment search]
    SearchLinear --> FindTicket[Find Existing Ticket<br/>Filter to SE team]
    FindTicket --> HasTicket{Linear Ticket Found?}
    HasTicket -->|No| Stop2([No Op])
    HasTicket -->|Yes| BuildMsg[Build Slack Message]
    BuildMsg --> PostSlack[Post to Slack<br/>Channel C09QT2RFSBW]
